3.2.1 AI Agent Workspace V3.0
To work with the UBP system I have developed and used several Google AI Studio APPs
this study series used a specific framework made to work autonomously and Agentic as
possible within the constraints of the platform available to me.
The Google AI Studio builds an environment for me to work in and can provide feedback
about issues I have operating it or add features I need as they arrive - an APP that
